Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.43,0:02:18.90,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(435,100)\fad(500,00)}「出現了！  因為是戰鬥少女」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.76,0:02:21.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是玉響咖啡廳的特製午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.98,0:02:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.61,0:02:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你們兩人的份
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.59,0:02:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就把剩下的端來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.91,0:02:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是傳說中的玉響午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得這午餐平時總是賣到缺貨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有這麼豐富的菜式呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:49.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀惠和麻音時間上來得及嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.84,0:02:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像記得你們午後要去購物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「沒關係」  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯然比起買東西  美味的玉響午餐更重要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這午餐很寶貴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為今天小啪提前拜託媽媽才終於能吃到的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  小啪親
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:13.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  你們能高興就再好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:17.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我也是第一次見的新品午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餐碟和裝點都很精緻  看上去真的很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:24.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.40,0:03:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.53,0:03:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香親來幫忙了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.50,0:03:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  香親  這午餐就由紀惠姐姐收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:36.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.49,0:03:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了  等很久了  等得我腿都軟了……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:43.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶  香親的推薦料理是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.86,0:03:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真會說啊   香親
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好勒  那就全部一口氣吃完
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.42,0:03:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香  來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:57.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們慢吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.06,0:04:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我也有個那樣可愛的弟弟就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是有哥哥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的老哥完全不可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這麼個哥哥一點都不會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:14.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快開始吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.65,0:04:18.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪  你不吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我覺得不想錯過「看上去很好吃」的這種心情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:44.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完之後的也要拍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.29,0:04:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得或許還留著「看上去很好吃」的這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:57.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜點是蜜桃果凍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.51,0:05:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃  看上去就涼涼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口吃上去蜜桃的香味就擴散開來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這好像不是普通的果凍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試著放了點葛根粉  有點和風的感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綿軟香滑好有夏天的感覺  好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告訴我這個的做法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.21,0:05:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  禮拜六下午怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.47,0:05:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是飯後茶  請喝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.09,0:05:40.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請喝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.01,0:05:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  香親
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個茶紀惠姐姐我就收下…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:52.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  香親端來的茶最好喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一杯  請務必親手幫我倒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:58.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太來勁了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.68,0:06:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.14,0:06:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香親  再見嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然比起哥哥  人生就該有個弟弟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人跟來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:44.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你這傢伙難道是小學生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是難道  我就是小學生啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我的名字叫做小町  不叫做你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.67,0:07:14.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  小町妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要跟著我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是所謂的跟蹤狂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是監視哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了保證你不再繼續做壞事的才隱蔽監視的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.43,0:07:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱蔽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:33.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監視
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.36,0:07:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是暴露了的話  就不叫做隱蔽監視了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  真是變幻莫測的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭剪刀布
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你輸了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的不算
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再比一次  行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:58.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦  已經分出勝負了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:08:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然輸了就要聽我的話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了我沒輸嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來比一次啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被她同化了  紀惠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼非得監視紀惠我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的詭計我全部看穿了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.02,0:08:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  詭計？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.88,0:08:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我可是知道你為了討好香君而特意去學甜點的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…香？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.66,0:08:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼非得像你說的那樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  你還裝蒜嗎  明明都輸給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒輸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:41.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再比一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:43.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心的話  就試著來追我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:51.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀惠  你把買東西的事忘了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.55,0:09:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你  小楓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最近的份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.46,0:09:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前午餐的照片嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼讓你在意的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  總覺得拍得不像我想的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拍得食物看上去感覺好吃可不是件容易事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maestro好像有在拍店裡的食物照片呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.29,0:09:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼訣竅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好試著著重於光影的使用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了  重要的是那種「很好吃」的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先試吃一下  然後融入「很好吃」的感覺來攝影或許會比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:10:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是吃掉了不就不能攝影了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.94,0:10:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不靠譜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪  接下來你打算做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.39,0:10:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  好像今天紀惠要來玉響咖啡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去玉響嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:33.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  蜜桃的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為約好了要奶奶教我之前那新款甜點的製作方法的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰親也會去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不準叫我薰親
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.55,0:10:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  小香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去玩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來請教這之前那款甜點的製作方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:10:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:03.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.50,0:11:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是跟香同年級的小町妹妹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.13,0:11:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  是紀惠認識的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該說是認識還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是正義的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會阻止你的詭計的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你  久等了  這是玫瑰果茶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  味道真好聞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顏色好美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不叫你這傢伙  我叫小町
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊  我就算了  要是給奶奶添麻煩就不好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,添麻煩的是你才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假裝向奶奶學甜點的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻去討好香君  好狡猾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  是那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.99,0:11:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.06,0:12:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就來比一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.41,0:12:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比一次？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我究竟誰能做出更好吃的甜點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.38,0:12:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來場甜點勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來一決高下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西不能拿來比吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經認輸了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才會輸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:18.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.15,0:12:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就來比吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.54,0:12:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全被小學生牽著鼻子走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀惠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你們倆就在這兒做甜點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.74,0:12:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就用做出來的東西來決勝負怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.68,0:12:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來判定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香回來的話就讓他來試吃判定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.38,0:12:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香親
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.96,0:12:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.57,0:12:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  好像準備完成了  預備
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:02.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀惠你要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:03.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜桃的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜桃果凍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那個好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要向奶奶學的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:16.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  並不是奶奶的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先按照自己的做法來試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:21.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  真能幹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是以西點師為目標的紀惠呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  小町還沒決定要做什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我能做的東西太多了  好難決定…呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  小町你喜歡薄烤餅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就試著做下薄烤餅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:14:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然奶奶這樣說的話我就做做看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就開始準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:19.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正等下要攪拌的  沒有打好也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.97,0:14:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放點糖好好攪拌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣  起白沫了就放牛奶進去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來放香草液和酸奶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後一起混合攪拌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:38.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麵粉要振動著撒下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.57,0:14:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攪拌的時候不要猶豫  乾脆一點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要沒有結塊就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.31,0:14:50.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜甜的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.15,0:14:55.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶的薄烤餅我和小香都很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:14:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:01.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是我贏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:08.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小町  差不多要翻面了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.75,0:15:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:19.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多用一個鍋鏟比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.25,0:15:21.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有點糊了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:28.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微烤過頭了點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.33,0:15:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  真遺憾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為薄烤餅什麼的很簡單呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.41,0:15:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很簡單哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:16:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是無論什麼甜點  想要做得好吃就有一件不能忘記的重要事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「好想給別人帶來美味」的那種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是最重要的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙在很努力地做著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來並不是想討好香君吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.21,0:16:31.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼接下來也要加油哦  小町
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  該翻面了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小町妹妹  笑得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是「好想給別人帶來美味」的那種感覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.95,0:17:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:09.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的要給香吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:12.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我再從頭開始做一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想給香君吃成品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.58,0:17:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好  那就開始準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小町是什麼時候開始在意香的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  4月的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.72,0:17:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是香搬來的時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.53,0:17:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開始還以為他是女生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:37.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道他是男孩子之後嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後就開始在意起他了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  涼下來後就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.24,0:17:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個也能烤好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做甜點時最重要的事情  小町你不是已經掌握了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外觀上兩邊都合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該回來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.14,0:18:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  平常都是這個時間回的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.68,0:18:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:18.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  小町你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你…好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香  兩個都吃吃看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就從薄烤餅開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這個我也開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼勝負呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香  兩邊都很好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.75,0:19:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩邊都好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.44,0:19:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多的程度？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:15.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打成平手了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的我都能吃完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.23,0:19:21.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.36,0:19:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我也來吃吃看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.90,0:19:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.34,0:19:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來來  盡情吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.84,0:19:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說「好吃」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.02,0:19:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個果凍  明明也是用的蜜桃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.91,0:19:54.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但感覺味道和奶奶做的那種不同  還真是獨特呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用皮和核來勾出味和色是要點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.12,0:20:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  紀惠為什麼要決定學做甜點的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.13,0:20:07.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別催我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:13.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前有一次我突然發燒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.52,0:20:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家庭旅行都因此取消了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.09,0:20:33.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我覺得是因為我才取消的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.59,0:20:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥一定會生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:42.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}二重燒，正式名稱是今川燒，別名大判燒，回轉燒，太鼓饅。豆沙餡的烤餅。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.25,0:20:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是二重燒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜甜的好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二重燒是紀惠喜歡的食物嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.67,0:20:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是哥哥喜歡的食物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:21:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他總是覺得自己喜歡的東西誰都會喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那時候吃的二重燒的味道忘不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.59,0:21:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我想肯定是希望讓人露出笑容的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.51,0:21:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把甜點變得甜蜜可口了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.83,0:21:19.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜的東西是用溫馨的感覺做成的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.37,0:21:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃嗎  小町
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.90,0:21:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  有著很溫馨的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:35.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才抱著「好想給別人帶來美味」的心情而努力的小町
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.63,0:21:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的露出了很溫柔的笑臉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.92,0:21:44.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃呢  薄烤餅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.46,0:21:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的話  好像能拍下有「很好吃」那種感覺的照片呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.45,0:22:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍得不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.30,0:22:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去是不是很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.00,0:22:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡這張
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.14,0:22:12.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「好想給別人帶來美味」的那份溫柔情感
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.57,0:22:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠給甜點帶來甜蜜美味的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:19.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什麼東西能夠給照片帶來美妙的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.14,0:22:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有趣的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.78,0:22:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味的東西能給製作的人和品嚐的人都帶來笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.82,0:22:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拍的照片若有一天能做到那樣  就太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.09,0:24:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來比一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.08,0:24:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用照片來討好很卑鄙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.56,0:24:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不允許
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.22,0:24:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.65,0:24:34.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  玉響～hitotose～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.27,0:24:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「因為是在等待漲潮的小島聽到的聲音」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
